    <string name="about_story">A modern, open-source revival of My Playlist Creator by Matt Duss — the little app Clip Sport owners relied on for a decade until it was abandoned and disappeared from the Play Store. This app writes the same byte-exact playlist format, rebuilt from scratch for today\'s Android. Not affiliated with or endorsed by the original author or SanDisk.</string>
